    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Nails designed so the top of the shank or a small head projects through a relatively broad, shallow, inverted-cup-shaped head; used for roofing and other purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
